    "description": "在 Aetheria 探索激动人心的冒险世界，带您踏上穿越不同种族和独特住宅的旅程。 在充满危险的世界中为生存而战，克服具有挑战性的障碍。 并开始执行任务，将你被遗忘的身份碎片拼凑起来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/ccb14c81fd156b090977f5e4bc2db3f3.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/ccb14c81fd156b090977f5e4bc2db3f3.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/ccb14c81fd156b090977f5e4bc2db3f3.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>踏上不懈的追求，击败各种强大的怪物，将自己推向极限，以登上权力和英勇的顶峰。 通过激烈的战斗，不断发展你的技能和经验，打造一条通往无与伦比的伟大之路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/10adfc9373e30bf3ff55595af9c4c475.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/10adfc9373e30bf3ff55595af9c4c475.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/10adfc9373e30bf3ff55595af9c4c475.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在艾瑟利亚，许多不同的怪物栖息在不同的区域，每个区域都有自己独特而强大的生物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/6158bfe051f102cff8c713805c4f3074.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/6158bfe051f102cff8c713805c4f3074.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/6158bfe051f102cff8c713805c4f3074.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与朋友联合起来对抗强大的头目，在一场史诗般的战斗中结合你的优势和技能。 你们将一起面对巨大的挑战，并坚强地对抗等待着的强大力量。 胜利在于友谊的纽带和团队合作的力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/8570c18bfad7a1c61b8c73b75580799a.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/8570c18bfad7a1c61b8c73b75580799a.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/8570c18bfad7a1c61b8c73b75580799a.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>掌握稀有武器并在 PvP 战斗中占据主导地位，超越你的朋友。 培养你的技能以统治至高无上，寻找独特的宝藏。 迎接挑战，让对手敬畏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/60c9597091bdb0ab8c612426077a3825.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/60c9597091bdb0ab8c612426077a3825.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/60c9597091bdb0ab8c612426077a3825.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在埃瑟利亚领域，获取铠甲所需的材料是必不可少的努力，因为它掌握着在广阔的疆域中增强力量和推进发展的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/8028a56f4e24cabcedee4b1d937a692d.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/8028a56f4e24cabcedee4b1d937a692d.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/8028a56f4e24cabcedee4b1d937a692d.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>逃离疲惫，深入Aetheria的境界，拥抱舒适，让宁静淹没你。 漫游、探索、从敌人那里收集经验并狩猎稀有武器，这是冒险真正流动的地方。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/aa6fbc104d830f07df0fa09456582ae4.poster.avif?t=1770637109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/aa6fbc104d830f07df0fa09456582ae4.webm?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/aa6fbc104d830f07df0fa09456582ae4.mp4?t=1770637109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
